# --- Standard G90XF calibration (SHIPPED in-repo; the same for every Odyssey 3D unit) ---
# The lenticular weave field (hub/_fields.pkl), correction textures (calib/3DStackCorrection_A/B.png),
# and the tracker/eye calibration are committed so the player gives clean glasses-free 3D out of the
# box -- no per-monitor capture. See CALIBRATION.md. Still ignored: the encrypted Samsung 3dstack blob
# (never read at runtime) and dev .npy intermediates.
calib/3dstack.eini
hub/_*.npy

# --- Large model weights (fetched by setup_linux.sh) ---
models/*.task
models/*.onnx
models/*.tflite

# --- Python / build / editor cruft ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.bak
.venv/
venv/
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Runtime / scratch ---
*.log
/tmp/

# --- Media (don't commit big test videos) ---
*.mp4
*.mkv
*.webm
*.mov
